01:33:30,487 --> 01:33:31,956
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

1007
01:33:32,488 --> 01:33:33,790
- Let's go.
- [CHUCKLES]

1008
01:34:01,651 --> 01:34:04,354
[RADIO CHATTER IN ARABIC]

